      ],
      "sc:description": "ekokrati computes habitat connectivity metrics (PC, IIC, EC(PC), dPC and its decomposition into intra-patch, flux and connector components) for habitat patch networks. Users upload polygon data as GeoPackage or shapefile, set species-specific dispersal parameters, and receive patch importance scores and landscape-level indices. Designed for conservation planners, landscape ecologists and environmental consultants. No installation required.",
      "sc:featureList": {
        "@id": "edam:operation_3927"
      },
